rows.name:
It's been so many years since
I started living here as a refugee
in Acedia...

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
What's it like?
I wake up, get my rations,
do my chores, and sleep. That's it.
[3]: Everyone says it's Superbia's fault for
coming to take Gula... Hey, you have
a Blade with you?!

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Everyone blames Superbia for
annexing Gula, and- Wait, are
those Blades with you?!

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0004
rows.name:
The Blade that burned my house down
is one of your kind, right?!
Down with Blades! Down with Blades!
